metadata.name: Combat Crate
metadata.description:
10KTF Combat Crates contain Level 2 Combat gear for Battle.town Missions. Once opened by an owner, the Blank Combat item will become part of the 10KTF Stockroom.

Equip your avatar with Combat gear to level up!

Bring your Blank Combat item and a 10KTF supported parent NFT to mint 1:1 Combat gear. Once minted, your Combat item will become part of the 10KTF collection.
